"taʿjabūna","e":"kamu heran"}],"a":{"g":"Then at this statement do you wonder?","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                وقال عز وجل: ﴿ أفمن هذا الحديث تعجبون وتضحكون ولا تبكون وأنتم سامدون ﴾ {} بل أقول كل ما ورد في فضل البكاء من خشية الله فهو إظهار لفضيلة الخشية فإن البكاء ثمرة الخشية فقد قال تعالى: ﴿ فليضحكوا قليلا وليبكوا كثيرا ﴾ {} وقال تعالى: ﴿ يبكون ويزيدهم خشوعا ﴾ {} وقال عز وجل: ﴿ أفمن هذا الحديث تعجبون وتضحكون ولا تبكون وأنتم سامدون ﴾ {}\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                Indeed, do you then wonder at this discourse [hadith], and laugh and do not weep, while you amuse yourselves [samidun]?\n\nRather, I say: All that has come regarding the virtue of weeping from fear of Allah [khashya] is a manifestation of the virtue of fear [khashya], for weeping is the fruit of fear [khashya]. Indeed, He, the Exalted, has said: \"So let them laugh a little and weep much.\" And He, the Exalted, has said: \"They weep, and it increases them in humility [khushu'].\" And He, the Mighty and Majestic, has said: \"Indeed, do you then wonder at this discourse [hadith], and laugh and do not weep, while you amuse yourselves [samidun]?\"\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"60":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.9","c":"وَتَضْحَكُونَ","d":"wataḍḥakūna","e":"dan kamu mentertawakan"},{"b":"1.6","h":"3.32","c":"وَلَا","d":"walā","e":"dan tidak"},{"b":"2.2","h":"4.41","c":"تَبْكُونَ","d":"tabkūna","e":"menangis"}],"a":{"g":"And you laugh and do not weep"}},"61":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.35","c":"وَأَنْتُمْ","d":"wa-antum","e":"dan kalian"},{"b":"2.0","h":"2.44","c":"سَامِدُونَ","d":"sāmidūna","e":"melengahkan"}],"a":{"g":"While you are proudly sporting?"}},"62":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.9","c":"فَاسْجُدُوا","d":"fa-us'judū","e":"maka bersujudlah"},{"b":"1.1","h":"2.61","c":"لِلَّهِ","d":"lillahi","e":"kepada Allah"},{"b":"2.4","h":"4.38","c":"وَاعْبُدُوا","d":"wa-uʿ'budū","e":"dan sembahlah (Dia)"}],"a":{"g":"So prostrate to Allah and worship [Him]."}}}